# 💇‍♂️ Salon Booking System — Project Guide

## 1️⃣ Features List (Minimum)

**Basic Features:**

1. Home page (About, Services, Contact)
2. Booking form (name, phone, date, barber)
3. List of barbers / stylists
4. Appointment confirmation

**Optional / Advanced Features:**

* Admin panel (appointments dekhne ke liye)
* Login system (user accounts)
* Email or WhatsApp confirmation
* Responsive design (mobile-friendly)

